name: The Queen and the King
description:
"The Queen and the King," 2022, MP4 video, 1920x1080, 16s
The Queen and the King saw themselves in one another.  They saw the world in similar ways, and their palace began to resemble what they saw in their collaborative dreams.  They fantasized and dreamed so much that the outside world became unrecognizable to them.  They did not want to leave their palace because nothing outside was as beautiful or as magical.  They died happily inside their palace while the rest of the world continued on, and simply forgot about them.
